Class Flow

  • java.lang.Object
    • uniol.apt.adt.extension.Extensible
      • uniol.apt.adt.Edge<PetriNet,Flow,Node>
        • uniol.apt.adt.pn.Flow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IExtensible, IEdge<PetriNet,Flow,Node>

    public class Flow
extends Edge<PetriNet,Flow,Node>
    A flow represents an edge of a petri net. It goes from one place to a transition or from one transition to a place. A flow can have a weight.
    Author:
    Dennis-Michael Borde, Manuel Gieseking
